                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <h5 class="text-white mt-5">Follow Us</h5>
                <ul class="fs-6 list-unstyled">
                    <li><a href="https://en-gb.facebook.com/Einzigtech-207465192613208/" target="_blank">Facebook</a></li>
                    <li><a href="https://twitter.com/einzigtech" target="_blank">Twitter</a></li>
                    <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/einzigtech" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
